<div class="main-content-controller">
  <h1 class="gradient-text gradient-text--large">About TaskFlow</h1>
  <h5 class="main-description">
    We believe that task management shouldn't be complicated. TaskFlow was created to help you focus on what matters most while keeping everything organized and beautiful.
  </h5>
</div>

<div class="main-goal feature">
  <%= image_tag("mission.png", alt: "Our Mission", size: "100x100", draggable: false, class: "feature___icon")%>
  <h5 class="feature___title">Our Mission</h5>
  <p class="feature___description">To create the most intuitive and beautiful task management tool that helps individuals and teams achieve their goals. We want to transform task management from a burden into a delightful experience that motivates you to be more productive.</p>
</div>
<div class="features-container">
  <div class="feature">
    <%= image_tag("karban.jpg", alt: "kanban", size: "80x80", draggable: false, class: "feature___icon")%>
    <h5 class="feature___title">Kanban Board</h5>
    <p class="feature___description">Visualize your workflow with our beautiful three-column board: To Do, In Progress, and Done.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature">
    <%= image_tag("authenticate.png", alt: "kanban", size: "80x80", draggable: false, class: "feature___icon")%>
    <h5 class="feature___title">Easy Authentication</h5>
    <p class="feature___description">Sign in effortlessly with Google OAuth or traditional email and password authentication.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature">
    <%= image_tag("thunder.png", alt: "Lightning Fast", size: "80x80", draggable: false, class: "feature___icon")%>
    <h5 class="feature___title">Lightning Fast</h5>
    <p class="feature___description">Built with modern technologies for instant loading and smooth interactions across all devices.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="main-goal feature main-goal--gradient last">
  <h5 class="feature___title">Ready To Get Started</h5>
  <p class="feature___description">Join thousands of users who trust TaskFlow for their productivity</p>
  <%= link_to "Sign Up NOw", "#", class: "btn btn--primary" %>
</div>
